								p For more than a decade, Jenna Loxterman has been a vital member of one of NAI Ohio Equities’ most successful teams, the Office Brokerage Group. She supports the team’s marketing, business development, and transaction management initiatives—efforts that have contributed to doubling its production over the same period.
								p Now as Senior Marketing Coordinator, Jenna collaborates closely with marketing leadership to execute campaigns that align with company goals. She also leads the Marketing Assistant team, overseeing project execution, streamlining workflows, and driving marketing performance.
